quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,"Haa, Miim"
  46,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, si wanaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mun]. Yeddu…ìe …ìen ko …óuurnii…ìe e ko …ìe rentiniraa kon"
  46,4,"Maaku: \"On yi'ii ko rewoton kon hara wanaa Allah, hollee lam ko …ói tagi e leydi ndin? Kaa hara hi…ói mari ge…ìal e [tagugol] kammuuli …óin? Awa addanee lam Deftere jippinaande ado ndee …óoo maa…óum batte ganndal, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  46,5,"Ko hommbo …ìuri majjude, wa on rewoowo ko wanaa Allah, kon ko jaabotaako mo haa √ëalnde Darngal? Hara …óin [rewetee…ói] ko welsindii…ói e dewal majji"
  46,6,"Si yim…ìe …ìen moo…ìoyaama [ka Darngal], …ói wontanoyay …ìe ay…ìe, …ìe wona e yeddugol ko …ìe rewaynoo…ói kon"
  46,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen …ìanngu…óe …óen janngaama e ma…ì…ìe, yedunoo…ìe goonga …ìen tuma nde arnoo e ma…ì…ìe …ìen wi'a: \"∆äum ko mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  46,8,"Kaa …ìe wi'ay woni :\"O fefindi nde?\" Awa maaku: \"Si taw mi fefindi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam huunde e [lepte] Allah …óen. Ko Kanko …ìuri anndude on, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko Kanko woni Haforowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  46,9,"Maaku: \"Mi wonaa arano e Nulaa…ìe …ìen; mi anndaa kadi ko wa…óetee mi, maa ko wa…óete…óon. Mi jokkaa si wanaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wanaa jertinoowo …ìanngina"
  46,10,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, yeddu…óon …óum, seedotoo…óo e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'ila …ìen seedii e [sellugol] …óum, o gom…óini, onon kan towniti…óon...Pellet, Allah fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"